**PLEASE READ BEFORE PURCHASING**

Our Petite range of budget stationery measures 4.5" x 5.6" and fits inside an A6 envelope, which are available in all sorts of colors at your local stationery store or you can add white ones to your order before you checkout.

The cardstock is bright white with a semi-gloss finish and 110lbs weight which is suitable for invitations.

We DO NOT advise you to choose the satin paper option as that is a much thinner 80lb paper, which is more akin to magazine pages than cardstock.

If you’d prefer a Classic 5×7 size invitation printed on 120lb cardstock with a matte finish you can transfer this design to a Flat Card using the transfer design options. Flat cards are not in the budget range but you have a wider choice of sizes and cardstock options and they ship with envelopes.

The shape and size best suited to the design will appear in the design transfer options.

If you make changes to the shape or size or choose another product and the design is cropped in any way or doesn’t look right on the page you will need to use the Live Design Service to have someone adjust the layout for you, unless you are comfortable doing it yourself.

There is no manual check or intervention between the placement of the order and the printing, so what you see on the screen is what will be printed and shipped to you.
